data.description: Nestled in the heart of Melbourne, this charming pool home offers a perfect blend of comfort and versatility. Step into your backyard and find yourself greeted by a sparkling pool, perfect for relaxation and recreation. The spacious patio area provides ample room for lounging and entertaining, making it ideal for family gatherings or quiet evenings under the stars. Adjacent to the pool, a separate structure serves as a bonus room retreat. Whether you envision a home office, a guest suite, a fitness center, or a creative studio, this versatile space provides the perfect canvas for bringing your vision to life. Inside, the home boasts modern updates including a 2024 HVAC system, a kitchen with newer appliances, countertops, and cabinets with ample storage space, making meal preparation a breeze. Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful pool home yours.
